{
  "name": "RPlog_Winter_Returns_to_NRS_Alderaan",
  "title": "Winter's Wounded Return",
  "summary": "Aboard the NRV Alderaan, the New Republic agent Winter limps back from a covert mission in a stolen shuttle, calling in a distress request and reporting two stunned guards, a wounded CSA captive, and an injured comrade. Princess Leia receives the call and, recognizing Winter as a close friend, asks the Jedi Jessalyn to accompany her to the docking bay. They meet the battered, exhausted Targeter, who maintains her cold composure long enough to ask after the missing General Solo before her injuries catch up with her. Mid-corridor, Winter collapses from extreme exhaustion, cracked ribs, and a concussion, and Jessalyn calls an emergency medical team. The medics rush Winter to the MedSuite, where Leia, sick with worry and reaching across the Force to Luke, watches as her friend is lowered into a bacta tank to begin healing.",
